He received the Ph.D. degree in physics from RWTH Aachen University, Aachen, Germany, in 2004., , Since 1995, he has been working at the Chair for Laser Technology (LLT) of RWTH Aachen University and at the Fraunhofer Institute for Laser Technology (ILT), Aachen.
